  "short_description": "Blue Fish Yokohama is a relaxing tile-based puzzle game. Play as a fish that eats miso ramen, cheese ramen and tantanmen by jumping, bumping, bouncing and splashing through a Japanese restaurant. Solve 50 handcrafted levels with unique game mechanics.",
