  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>----------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2026 Update </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI redesign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New environmental effects</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blue Fish Yokohama is a relaxing tile-based puzzle game where all the ramen is deliciously eaten by our protagonist... a fish!?!!?!?!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What's on the menu?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/a4cc9cd60fae42cc3d560feaab905da3.avif?t=1774035878\" width=425 height=103 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Cheese ramen is sticky and fat so you don't jump so far. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Miso ramen has that umami boost. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Spicy hot tantanmen will blow you away. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Mizu Yokan is your bouncy dessert. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Simple controls that you will pick up instantly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/8b2537998d51e5e873ae32226bf78ae7.poster.avif?t=1774035878\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/8b2537998d51e5e873ae32226bf78ae7.webm?t=1774035878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/8b2537998d51e5e873ae32226bf78ae7.mp4?t=1774035878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Discover new and exciting game mechanics as the levels progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/57e53571f5e0e7037dbf0cfa6444e5e9.poster.avif?t=1774035878\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/57e53571f5e0e7037dbf0cfa6444e5e9.webm?t=1774035878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/57e53571f5e0e7037dbf0cfa6444e5e9.mp4?t=1774035878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Solve & explore 50 handcrafted levels in beautiful and colorful voxel art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/1617f463613f0e2cff7c89675ab6154d.poster.avif?t=1774035878\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/1617f463613f0e2cff7c89675ab6154d.webm?t=1774035878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/1617f463613f0e2cff7c89675ab6154d.mp4?t=1774035878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat the ramen, save the world.<br><br>You'll receive the full game with the 50 levels plus loads of karma points for supporting independent & small-scale developers.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>----------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2026 Update </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI redesign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New environmental effects</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blue Fish Yokohama is a relaxing tile-based puzzle game where all the ramen is deliciously eaten by our protagonist... a fish!?!!?!?!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What's on the menu?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/a4cc9cd60fae42cc3d560feaab905da3.avif?t=1774035878\" width=425 height=103 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Cheese ramen is sticky and fat so you don't jump so far. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Miso ramen has that umami boost. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Spicy hot tantanmen will blow you away. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Mizu Yokan is your bouncy dessert. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Simple controls that you will pick up instantly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/8b2537998d51e5e873ae32226bf78ae7.poster.avif?t=1774035878\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/8b2537998d51e5e873ae32226bf78ae7.webm?t=1774035878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716500/extras/8b2537998d51e5e873ae32226b